entries.femaleVariant: Nah, I don't like it. Them payin' us by the hour, not by the job.
Choom, what's your deal? Job's gonna stretch out for months. Gig of a lifetime!
Yeah, and you know who's buildin' it? Asukaga & Finch. Finance.
An' if someone's in finance and starts buildin' all a sudden, means somethin' stinks.
Even if it does, so what? You got a gig? You got one.
Rather know my hands weren't launderin' someone else's eddies.
Even got insurance... Fuckin' luxury investment. Nah, total front.
